Agricultural land use impacts aquatic greenhouse gas emissions from wetlands in the Canadian Prairie Pothole Region
</a>
</h2>

<p><img src="/assets/images/ppr-cropped-wetland-landscape.jpg" caption="" position="left" align="left" width="45%" style="padding: 10px 15px 0px 0px; clip-path: rect(10% 95% 100% 0 round 10px);" /></p>

<p>
This dataset presents a survey of greenhouse gas content, emissions rates, and biogeochemical features of open water wetland habitats in the three prairie provinces of the Canadian Prairies. A subset of the data have been previously published by Soued et al. 2024. Nature Communications, but this dataset is revised to correct for a minor error.
</p>

